reviewText: I watched this movie not long after it came out and loved it. I wanted to see it again. So I searched it and decided to purchase it, at a great price.

I very much enjoyed Ivana Trump's character, the plot truthfully shows how women will need to find strength in a challenging  world of
fateful falls and disappointments. I felt the film was done very artfully.
I rate this enjoyable love story with Five Stars.
